author: klute
msg: Fixed a bug where the logical comparison of two sections returned false only because one of them had property 1 (codepage) and the other had not. Now two sections are equal if their property values are equal disregarding property 1.

author: klute
msg: Restored the functionality to use ALL files beginning with "Test" in src/testcases/org/apache/poi/hpsf/data as test data. Each of these files is read and rewritten. The result is compared with the original and must be equal to it.

author: klute
msg: Fixed a bug where a mutable section's format ID was written in the wrong byte order. Thanks to Bernd Freigang for pointing this out!

author: klute
msg: Made it explicit that you need J2SE 1.4 or better for a reasonable codepage support.
